{"tid":935823,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以解釋下點解支那人嗰樣都一樣","createTime":"2018-12-10T10:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T10:52:21.000Z","uid":101560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8027eea7d7e526741a9d070157be71c641f3f6","tid":935823,"uid":101560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"支那人真係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑黑實實，塊面唔會光滑，重點係面頰一定紅紅地。之後單眼皮細長眼，雙眼無神。男人平頭，女人就黑馬尾or短頭髮，而且全部人個頭都好油。無論四季都著到好厚，顏色一係土灰色，一係就好鮮豔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行為上：搭電梯一定企右邊，排隊係亂排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一堆支人嗰樣都一樣，就好似我睇黑人咁全部一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b707772b16358d44751409a662cf36737dda99","tid":935823,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:21:25.000Z","msg":"支那人真係特別柒"},{"pid":"de0206beef1bf962da6eb198994082bee87d5d6b","tid":935823,"uid":64374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}